search_results.title: Jo Jackson: books, biography, latest update
search_results.snippet: Jo Jackson is the author of three novels and a novella. She was born in Birmingham UK. She was a nurse and midwife before becoming a family psychotherapist.

search_results.title: Meet the Author: Beyond the Margin by Jo Jackson
search_results.snippet: My name is Jo Jackson. I am the author of two books, 'Too Loud a Silence' published in 2016 and 'Beyond the Margin' published in 2019.
